{
  "title": "Pazeh a rutudaw a kakanēn",
  "titleCh": "巴宰的傳統飲食",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "巴宰族人的傳統飲食有阿拉粿，阿拉粿是用糯米艾草與糕混合包成，內餡有甜和鹹兩種口味。醃製的有 : 魚給、肉給、醬筍，芥菜可以製成酸菜、 菜乾，蘿蔔可以製成蘿蔔絲、蘿蔔乾，竹筍可以製成多樣產品，這些都是用鹽巴醃漬，能保存很久。",
      "ab": "rinutudaw Pazeh saw a kakanēn ka hada umu. umu ka kalu pazay iu ngarungar minurimat kipudun. rizikan ka hada makēlēm iu tuxubus dusa a bangazi. inumas ka hada alaw rumut iu tubēhē awnu muburiak makēlēm a tubēhē. pinaridax a tubēhē. saipu awnu muburiak saipuha. si saipuha iu ali aunu muburiak saysay. imini dadua ka inumas kinalu pahar. aunu madu masēzēm ha e.",
